Description: Keep your business essentials neatly stowed and at your fingertips in the McKlein USA Lakewood -Fly-Through Checkpoint-Friendly Removable Rolling Ladies' Briefcase. This luxurious Italian leather bag features a secure, removable, padded laptop computer sleeve and a spacious main compartment divided by a secure zippered pocket with plenty of room for your files, documents, brochures, change of clothing, cosmetics, toiletries, and anything else you need throughout the busy day or on an overnight trip. An interior organizer section contains credit/business card slots, a key clip, pen loops, and open pockets for your cell phone and notepad. The McKlein USA Lakewood -Fly-Through Checkpoint-Friendly Removable Rolling Ladies' Briefcase has a patented 2-in-1 Removable Wheel and Handle System, a telescopic handle, and a shoulder strap for carrying versatility and maneuvering ease.
